================================================================================

	ALGRAEPH CHANGES

================================================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Bugs fixed:

- Import error in pubsub.py in combination with wxPython 2.8.11.0
- Drawing truncated at right side because margin was too small
- Syntax error in Graphiz spec for marking focused nodes

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Bugs fixed:

- Node labels containing double quotes crashed Graphviz
- Empty corpus caused crash
- Alpino format: an error message is raised when a graph in graphbank in empty

New features:

- New and faster implementation of reading/writing corpusfiles 
- Support for new XML format for a corpus 
- The default extension for a parallel graph corpus is now ".pgc"
- Alpino format only: new option to automatically fold nodes aligned 
  with relation "equals"
- Alpino format only: shortcut keys for the standard Daeso relations



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.6.0
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- first public release of Algraeph